RILLED/FRIED ASSORTMENT(SHARED) Kampachi Shima-Aji Flying Fish(Fried head and Body) We got down and dirty with this one, leaving no survivors!  SALMON CARPACCIO(1pc.) TAKUANTORO(2pc) AMAEBI(1pc.) All excellent!  Eric capped it off with a Western Style SURF AND TURF ROLL Shrimp Tempura Roll topped with Australian Wagyu Beef, and garnished with Crispy Onions, Micro Greens, Yum yum Sauce, and Nori Flakes. Great end to the meal which cost as much as a nigiri dinner at that very popular sushi joint next to Trattoria Nakamura-Ya...  . We all finished with Banana Tempura Ice Cream, and after our meal Eric  had a toast with everyone with a pretty pricey sake. What a great evening ....Good Food, Good Friends, Good Fun....ALOHA!!!  #366/365...ONE MORE FOR LEAP YEAR!!!!!!! CHEEEEEHOOOO!!!!
